 SYSTEM DESIGN AND FEATURES
----------------------------
 The Main Features are:

1. Full calender/diary/planner facilities.
2. Creation of categories of entries - e.g. bills,birthdays,letters to be
   written,notepad.
3. Sorting of appointments by date and time of day.
4. Urgent Notice board.
5. Overdue notice board.
6. One week's advance notice of forthcoming events.
7. Single entry of an event over a range of days/weeks/months.
8. Updating of regular appointments over a range
9. Comprehensive search facility for related entries.
10. Automatic reminders of messages/appointments that are urgent,overdue
    and in the forthcoming week.
11. Month and week summary at a glance, indicating times booked and free.
12. Print option.
13. Grouping of related messages.
14. Month Planner.
15. Week Planner.
16. Day Planner.
17. Upto 1,000 messages.



