 WHEN FIRST ENTERING DAY-BY-DAY
-------------------------------
 When you first load DAY-BY-DAY, you will be prompted to enter the current
date.
 DAY-BY-DAY will also display the date that the program was last used (if
information was saved).

 AUTOMATIC REMINDERS

 Having entered the current date, messages will appear in the following
order. Simply select FORWARD to scroll through the different categories
(alternatively just select EXIT to go straight to the main menu).

 Urgent messages: This special category is provided for those messages
 which you want displayed every time you load DAY-BY-DAY.

 Overdue: All overdue messages.

 This Week: All messages for today and the following six days.

Any of the above categories may also be selected from the main menu.



